originalText.text: Dr. Malek is exactly who you’d want to do your first root canal. I have a long history of dental work and was really assured by his depth of knowledge, his desire and willingness to explain and answer questions (a true teacher) and competency! He was so great at making me feel comfortable and I would recommend anyone to come see him. I hope to never have another root canal, but if I do, I know I am safe in his hands. Very smart, warm and personable.

originalText.text: Fantastic experience with my root canal by Doctor Malek and his team at Sutton Place Dental. Even if I had been nervous, his calm demeanor, thorough explanations and steady hands made the procedure effortless and without stress. Highly recommended and I know I'll be in great hands if I need his services again.

originalText.text: I was dreading my first root canal but with the gentle and professional care that Dr Malek provided along with his kindness in talking me through the procedure it was an exceptional experience. I highly recommend Dr Malek and I tell people that a root canal should not be dreaded at all under his excellent care.

originalText.text:
I had a great experience getting my first root canal with Doctor Malek and his team at east 56th Street. I was nervous it would hurt during or post, but the process was actually smooth, fast and painless once the anesthesia kicked in.
I was also very pleased with Doctor Malek's bedside manner. He explains everything thoroughly with kindness and patience. Highly recommend him.
